      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 60,
      "message": "What is this if condition for? Can you please explain the intent?\n\nUsually logging framework log only if the method ( debug ) is higher or same as the configured level. So, log.debug will log if log level is either DEBUG or TRACE.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 7680,
        "name": "Renu Kumari",
        "display_name": "Renu Kumari",
